      <body>
         <head>Ariel</head>
         <p xml:id="ariel_dedication">(for <persName ref="#Alvarez">Al</persName>)</p>
         <lg rend="right-align">
            <l>Stasis in darkness.</l>
            <l>Then the substanceless blue  </l> 
            <l>Pour of tor and distances.</l>
         </lg> 
         <lg rend="right-align">
         <l>God’s Lioness!</l>   
         <l>How one we grow!</l>
         <l>Pivot of heels and knees! The furrow</l>
         </lg>
         <lg rend="right-align">
         <l>Splits and passes, sister to   </l>
         <l>The brown arc</l>
         <l>Of the neck I cannot catch,</l>
         </lg >
         <lg rend="right-align">
            <l>Nigger-eye   </l>
            <l>Berries cast dark</l>
            <l>Hooks—</l>
         </lg>
         <lg rend="right-align">
            <l>Black sweet blood mouthfuls!</l>   
            <l>Shadows!</l>
            <l>Something else</l>
         </lg>
         <lg rend="right-align">
            <l>Hauls me through air—</l>
            <l> Thighs, hair;</l>
            <l>Flakes from my heels.</l>
         </lg>
         <lg rend="right-align">
            <l>White</l>
            <l>Godiva, I unpeel—</l>
            <l>Dead hands, dead stringencies!</l>
         </lg>
         <lg rend="right-align">
         <l>And now I</l>
         <l>Foam to wheat, a glitter of seas.   </l>
         <l>The child’s cry</l>
         </lg>
         <lg rend="right-align">
            <l>Melts in the wall. </l>         
            <l>And I</l>
            <l>Am the arrow,</l>
         </lg>
         <lg rend="right-align">
            <l>The dew that flies</l>
            <l>Suicidal, at one with the drive</l>   
            <l>Into the red</l>
         </lg>
         <l rend="right-align">Eye, the cauldron of morning.</l>
         
         <p xml:id="ariel_signature"><persName ref="Sylvia Plath"> -Sylvia Plath- </persName> </p>
